Discover Service Capabilities with My Service Journey (Beta)

Discover how to take your Service Cloud implementation from good to great with My Service Journey. Get the Salesforce point of view on how to achieve your business goals for different Service areas, like the Help Site or Agent Console.

Where: This change applies to Lightning Experience in Enterprise and Unlimited editions.

This feature is a Beta Service. Any use of the Beta Service is subject to the applicable Beta Services Terms provided at Agreements and Terms.

How: Launch My Service Journey from the App Launcher. Add My Service Journey to your console app’s navigation menu for enhanced exploration of Service Cloud capabilities.
